      "text": "Quiz Nanairo Dreams: Nijiiro-chō no Kiseki (Japanese: クイズなないろDREAMS 虹色町の奇跡; \"Quiz Seven Color Dreams - Miracle of Rainbow Color Village\") is a Japanese video game developed by Capcom. The game is a hybrid of a quiz game and a dating sim.\nIt was released in 1996 originally for the arcade game running on the CP System II platform, and was then released for the PlayStation and Sega Saturn systems in 1997.",
